<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('../partials/head', { pageTitle: 'GDPR Compliance' }) %>
  <style>
    .legal-main {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 60px auto 40px auto;
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      border-top: 6px solid #ff6600;
    }
    .legal-main h1 {
      color: #ff6600;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.2em;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
    }
    .legal-main h2 {
      color: #222;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-top: 2em;
      margin-bottom: 0.7em;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-left: 4px solid #ff6600;
      padding-left: 0.6em;
      background: #f9f6f2;
    }
    .legal-main ul {
      margin-left: 1.2em;
      margin-bottom: 1.2em;
    }
    .legal-main p {
      margin-bottom: 1.1em;
      color: #444;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/header') %>
  <div style="height:32px;"></div>
  <main class="legal-main">
    <h1>GDPR Compliance</h1>
    <p>NomadProHub is committed to protecting your data and complying with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).</p>
    <h2>Your Rights Under GDPR</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Right to access your data</li>
      <li>Right to rectification</li>
      <li>Right to erasure</li>
      <li>Right to restrict processing</li>
      <li>Right to data portability</li>
      <li>Right to object</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>We process your data based on your consent, contractual necessity, and legal obligations.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We retain your personal data only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes for which it was collected or as required by law.</p>
    <h2>Data Transfers</h2>
    <p>Your data may be transferred and stored outside the EU/EEA. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place for such transfers.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:2em;font-size:0.95em;color:#888;">Last updated: August 10, 2025</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>To exercise your rights or for questions, email support@nomadprohub.com.</p>
    <h2>User Definition</h2>
    <p>For GDPR purposes, the only registered user is the site admin or owner. All other visitors access NomadProHub for public viewing and do not create accounts or profiles.</p>
  </main>
  <div style="height:32px;"></div>
  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
